<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Submission Success</title>
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: gilroy, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        body {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: rgba(45, 167, 167, 0.404);
        }
        .result-box {
            background-color: #87cbcbd4;
            width: 80%;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.7rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .result-box h2 {
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }
        .result-box p {
            margin: 0 1rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        a {
            display: inline-block;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background-color: #207171d4;
            color: aliceblue;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: #1a6262;
        }
        @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
            .result-box {
                width: 28rem;
                border-radius: 1rem;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }
            .result-box h2 {
                margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="result-box">
        <h2>Hey, <%= username %>!</h2>
        <p>You're studying at <%= college %>, in the <%= dept %> department, and in your <%= year %> year!</p>
        <p>You love <%= hobby %>? That's awesome!</p>
        <p>Submitted on: <%= date %></p>
        <a href="/">Try Again</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>